Package cz.zcu.kiv.dfs_simulator.helpers

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    SimulationThroughputHistoryReducer
    An interface for history throughput samples reducers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AllInclusiveThroughputHistoryReducer
    Implementation of SimulationThroughputHistoryReducer that actually doesn't do any reducing, method reduce returns original data.
    DouglasPeuckerThroughputHistoryReducer
    Implementation of SimulationThroughputHistoryReducer that uses Ramer-Douglas-Peucker algorithm for reduction https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ramer%E2%80%93Douglas%E2%80%93Peucker_algorithm
    FxHelper
    General purpose methods related to GUI.
    Helper
    General purpose methods.
    MovingAverageReducer
    Implementation of SimulationThroughputHistoryReducer that reduces multiple samples into one using average of those samples.
    Pair<T,U>
    Simple key-value container.
    RadialDistanceThroughputHistoryReducer  
    SimulatorPreferences
    Provides basic functionality regarding user's preferences.
